{"name":"Inspiring Marshal Stance","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You become a brilliant example of dedication and poise in battle, encouraging your allies to follow suit.</p>\n<p>When you spend this action, attempt a @Check[type:diplomacy|dc:@self.level] check. The DC is usually a standard-difficulty DC of your level, but the GM can assign a different DC based on the circumstances. The effect depends on the result of your check.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> Your @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feat-effects.KBEJVRrie2JTHWIK]{Marshal's Aura} increases to a @Template[type:emanation|distance:20] and grants you and allies a +1 status bonus to attack rolls and saves against mental effects.<br />@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-better-marshal-aura.bma-effects.5PUxykTBVMfD7Yw4]{Inspiring Marshal Stance (Critical)}</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> As critical success, but your aura's size doesn't increase.<br />@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-better-marshal-aura.bma-effects.SuOwJZSvrYJWqxAB]{Inspiring Marshal Stance}</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> You fail to enter the stance.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> You fail to enter the stance and can't take this action again for 1 minute.<br />@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-better-marshal-aura.bma-effects.CwqCfXLuPvauRwHl]{Effect: Dull Marshal}</p>"},"source":{"value":"Pathfinder Advanced Player's Guide"},"rules":[],"slug":"inspiring-marshal-stance","schema":{"version":0.833,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":4},"traits":{"value":["archetype","open","stance"],"rarity":"common"},"featType":{"value":"archetype"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Marshal Dedication"},{"value":"trained in Diplomacy"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","ownership":{"default":0,"2PFR8A9AJIagAdyx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.llHrUtnTOsH3kdFX"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVers